thread.title: jesse reznicek

author: jesse reznicek
title: jesse reznicek
text:
I ONLY did a search for "Storage Units in My area" and a page loaded with Countless properties showed up. I found a space that was large enough to hold my belongings and EVEN My 2 smaller units that I have for Tools and other Furniture, including my Baby Grand Piano. 1 Unit, 1 price, 1 place and saving $240.00 per MONTH. You CANNOT put a Price on Convenience.
The Quality of Customer Service and Assistance that I received on the Phone was EXCEPTIONAL!
